 "replies": 37, "id": 910025}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 196290, "footer": "", "header": "一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340", "stars": 3685, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 234020, "username": "angcz", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/angcz", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/da1c2d8fc2127697a27eaec65cfbbaac?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/da1c2d8fc2127697a27eaec65cfbbaac?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/da1c2d8fc2127697a27eaec65cfbbaac?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1496649725, "last_modified": 1496904983}, "last_reply_by": "seaiaddca", "last_touched": 1674237661, "title": "有没有好吃 吃起来方便 饱肚子 健康的食物推荐？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/910081", "created": 1674217189, "deleted": 0, "content": "rt 靴靴各位", "content_rendered": "rt 靴靴各位", "last_modified": 1674217189, "replies": 35, "id": 910081}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_large.png?m=1660301119", "name": "create", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_normal.png?m=1660301119", "title": "分享创造", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/create", "topics": 19251, "footer": "", "header": "欢迎你在这里发布自己的最新作品！", "title_alternative": "Create", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_mini.png?m=1660301119", "stars": 4702, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 17, "parent_node_name": "geek"}, "member": {"id": 69817, "username": "greensea", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/greensea", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "greensea", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/39f8/b1c3/69817_mini.png?m=1520395668", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/39f8/b1c3/69817_normal.png?m=1520395668", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/39f8/b1c3/69817_large.png?m=1520395668", "created": 1407132601, "last_modified": 1520395668}, "last_reply_by": "wyf001912hp", "last_touched": 1674238379, "title": "wCaptcha, 一个基于工作量证明的 CAPTCHA", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/910042", "created": 1674196746, "deleted": 0, "content": "CAPTCHA 就是所谓的验证码，不过这个基于工作量证明的验证码可以不要求用户进行操作，在后台就可以默默地完成。\r\n\r\n这个验证码的核心在于，用工作量证明的方式取代了要求用户进行一些操作，来证明客户端是一个人类。不过这个验证码其实并不能区分客户端是不是人类，它的主要目的是防止大量的恶意请求，比如爆破用户名密码、爬虫之类。\r\n\r\n对于一个普通用户来说，花几秒钟的时间做一个计算，然后再提交表单，这是完全可以接受的，可是对于爬虫或者登录接口爆破之类的机器人来说，如果每发一个请求就要花两三秒的 CPU 时间，这就完全不可接受了。\r\n\r\n工作量证明算法使用了不可并行加速的算法，也就是说，显卡加速是废的，多核计算也是废的（除非同时对一个接口发送多个请求，但这样的请求是非正常的，很容易过滤掉）。\r\n\r\n网站在这里： https://wcaptcha.pingflash.com\r\n如果担心数据安全，可以直接用源码私有化部署。\r\n\r\n至于算法细节之类的东西，都可以在网站上找到，我就不在这里废话了。", "content_rendered": "<p>CAPTCHA 就是所谓的验证码，不过这个基于工作量证明的验证码可以不要求用户进行操作，在后台就可以默默地完成。</p>\n<p>这个验证码的核心在于，用工作量证明的方式取代了要求用户进行一些操作，来证明客户端是一个人类。不过这个验证码其实并不能区分客户端是不是人类，它的主要目的是防止大量的恶意请求，比如爆破用户名密码、爬虫之类。</p>\n<p>对于一个普通用户来说，花几秒钟的时间做一个计算，然后再提交表单，这是完全可以接受的，可是对于爬虫或者登录接口爆破之类的机器人来说，如果每发一个请求就要花两三秒的 CPU 时间，这就完全不可接受了。</p>\n<p>工作量证明算法使用了不可并行加速的算法，也就是说，显卡加速是废的，多核计算也是废的（除非同时对一个接口发送多个请求，但这样的请求是非正常的，很容易过滤掉）。</p>\n<p>网站在这里： <a href=\"https://wcaptcha.pingflash.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://wcaptcha.pingflash.com</a>\n如果担心数据安全，可以直接用源码私有化部署。</p>\n<p>至于算法细节之类的东西，都可以在网站上找到，我就不在这里废话了。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1674196746, "replies": 29, "id": 910042}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1673261684", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1673261684", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 53026, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1673261684", "stars": 8166, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 591282, "username": "spr1ngs", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/spr1ngs", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/c946c72bed3af7c6d0d7d6bde089a391?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/c946c72bed3af7c6d0d7d6bde089a391?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/c946c72bed3af7c6d0d7d6bde089a391?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1660551727, "last_modified": 1660551727}, "last_reply_by": "irytu", "last_touched": 1674207854, "title": "服务最好是无状态的是什么意思", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/910002", "created": 1674181236, "deleted": 0, "content": "有懂的大哥吗", "content_rendered": "<p>有懂的大哥吗</p>\n", "last_modified": 1674181236, "replies": 27, "id": 910002}]